{"tid":2228760,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢人船P，窮撚勿入","createTime":"2020-10-03T22:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T12:23:26.000Z","uid":369040,"like":55,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b5974c39ce2b04f0351c7d12bd37dade242988aa","tid":2228760,"uid":369040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T22:37:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個星期日，我唔去浦了。一早出海。 <br />\n我地book 了3 隻船。第一隻尼米茲級航空母艦，買的<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2zOVXNQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zOVXNQ.jpg&h=684efcf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxWTKsG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuxWTKsG.jpg&h=d72d138f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28vxfzm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28vxfzm.jpg&h=3f701537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐五千人的，長一千幾呎。 <br />\n順便請咗私人教練，可以試揸F18戰機，觀賞西貢牛尾海一帶景色<br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的二手運砂船，坐30人，工業風遊艇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZG8ymg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZG8ymg.jpg&h=0e82c46e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8dV9hNX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8dV9hNX.jpg&h=d1b9a085&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFiyKsX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFiyKsX.jpg&h=26957946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我中意呢隻多d，入少少，寫意d。 <br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通 中式船。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HCNWHe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHCNWHe5.jpg&h=f97ad295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞手會買好多酒。 <br />\n<br />\n星期日 , 7點尖沙咀碼頭集合 <br />\n<br />\n男仔：$1000 位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女仔：Model , 靚女免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通女仔：唔俾去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起$1000去船河的人吧。 <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d船河無得賺，<strong><em>搞手只求平安回航</em></strong>，大家開開心心玩返日。"},{"pid":"eed7a56ddaaea3100d69cf0a791da331d3d52aa8","tid":2228760,"uid":186431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T22:58:01.000Z","msg":"船上有無百家樂？有無按摩叫雞呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7bbaec491a2f416bec53a0845100230d5f6287","tid":2228760,"uid":307195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T22:59:15.000Z","msg":"窮撚想join<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41479ee3cfda46b70214d07b187a03f9b6f41af9","tid":2228760,"uid":157793,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T23:18:24.000Z","msg":"依隻真係royal級！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5b7832b7d700c49a66ba16b2ae96a2626929ef","tid":2228760,"uid":326287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e45ca0ea25ee329b6f81dcf7a4d24b7de6044b","tid":2228760,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n海上流動沙灘"},{"pid":"e608620be34ffb214445e02d8415b6181b8399c5","tid":2228760,"uid":54973,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:33:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e4f38ad003710e74a84c2fba98d1c2c63acec98","tid":2228760,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:34:37.000Z","msg